Summarize the store: sessions, events, disk usage, largest sessions (Area 3)

Usage: hh stats [OPTIONS]

Options:
      --top <TOP>  Number of largest sessions (by event count) to list [default: 5]
      --json       Emit machine-readable JSON instead of a table
  -h, --help       Print help

Example:
  hh stats
  hh stats --json
  hh stats --top 10
